[Teleport to Hunting Grounds]
You may teleport to any of the following hunting locations. Each teleport requires a sum of AA.
The Saint's Necropolis (70-80) - 76000 AA
Disciples Necropolis (70-80) - 11000 AA


Catacomb of Dark Omens (70-80) - 51000 AA
Catacomb of the Forbidden Path (70-80) - 40000 AA
